                                 <q xml:lang="gez">ገድለ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9744Victor">ፊቂጦር፡</persName>  ዘ<placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0101MadhaneAlam">ቅዱስ፡ መድኃኔ፡ ዓለም።</placeName>
